Z4 implements algorithms and techniques described in academic literature
including but not limited to:

- MiniSat (Een & Sorensson, 2003)
- DPLL(T) framework (de Moura & Bjorner, 2008)
- CaDiCaL techniques (Biere, 2021)
- SMT-LIB 2.6 standard
